23 WHEREAS, on June 9, 1995, six-year-old Morgan Chauntel Nick was
24 kidnapped from a little league baseball game in Alma, Arkansas, and a massive
25 state and federal law enforcement investigation ensued and continues, as
26 Morgan Nick remains missing; and
27
28 WHEREAS, June 9, 2025, will mark the thirtieth anniversary of the
29 kidnapping and disappearance of Morgan Nick; and
30
31 WHEREAS, Morgan's mother, Colleen Nick, formed the Morgan Nick
32 Foundation in 1996 and serves as full-time Executive Director of the
33 foundation; and
34
35 WHEREAS, the Morgan Nick Foundation believes that to reduce the number
36 of child abductions, children must be educated and empowered with the skills
